## `packages/tools/biome-plugins/no-object-assign.grit`

```grit
`$fn($args)` where {
    $fn <: `Object.assign`,
    register_diagnostic(
        span = $fn,
        message = "Prefer object spread instead of Object.assign()",
        severity = "warn"
    )
}
```

